                Nymphis Geminis <lb n="2"/>sacrum <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Fufius Gemini <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Politicus <lb n="5"/>idem aquam perduxit
